{"id":"edition-interpretive","lang":"grc","html":"<div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>Ἅπασα γε̑α καὶ πλατοὶς ἀὴρ <br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>γενᾷ σοι θάνατε <br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ἐξαπίνης μου τὸ βρέφος ἥρπασε[ς ἦ] <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>τίς ἀνάκη εἰ γὰρ ἐγήρα, οὐχεί σον [ἦν] <br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>☧ ἐγενήθη ὁ κύρις Ἀγάθων <span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">π͡ρ</span>(ὸ) ιε´ ☧ <br id=\"al6-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">6</span>καλανδῶν Νοενβρίων ἡμέρᾳ Κρό[νου] <br id=\"al7-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">7</span>ἔζη(σεν) <span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">μ͡ῆ</span>(νας) · ι´ · ἀπέθανε <span class=\"petraeligature\" title=\"Ligature: these characters are joined\">π͡ρ</span>(ὸ) · ι´ · [<span dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---</span>] καλανδῶν Σεπτενβρ[ίων] <br id=\"al8-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">8</span>ἡμέρᾳ Ἡλίου κυρία Ἀγάθη εἰρήνην Ἀγά[θωνι] </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p>"}